00044 void CHPQuantificationFileWriterTest::WriteTest()
00045 {
00046         ParameterNameValueTypeList params;
00047         ParameterNameValueType param;
00048 
00049         CHPQuantificationData data("CHP_quantification_file");
00050 
00051         data.SetAlgName(L"sig");
00052         data.SetAlgVersion(L"1.0");
00053         data.SetArrayType(L"test3");
00054         data.SetEntryCount(2, 10);
00055 
00056         param.SetName(L"an1");
00057         param.SetValueText(L"av1");
00058         params.push_back(param);
00059         data.AddAlgParams(params);
00060 
00061         params.clear();
00062         param.SetName(L"sn1");
00063         param.SetValueText(L"sv1");
00064         params.push_back(param);
00065         data.AddSummaryParams(params);
00066 
00067 
00068         CHPQuantificationFileWriter *writer = new CHPQuantificationFileWriter(data);
00069         affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetQuantificationData e;
00070 
00071         writer->SeekToDataSet();
00072         e.name = "abc";
00073         e.quantification = 10.0f;
00074         writer->WriteEntry(e);
00075         e.name = "xyz";
00076         e.quantification = 20.0f;
00077         writer->WriteEntry(e);
00078 
00079         delete writer;
00080 
00081         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(1);
00082 
00083 
00084 
00085 
00086         CHPQuantificationData data2;
00087         CHPQuantificationFileReader reader;
00088         reader.SetFilename("CHP_quantification_file");
00089         reader.Read(data2);
00090 
00091         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetAlgName() == L"sig");
00092         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetAlgVersion() == L"1.0");
00093         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetArrayType() == L"test3");
00094         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetEntryCount() == 2);
00095 
00096         ParameterNameValueTypeList p = data2.GetAlgParams();
00097         ParameterNameValueTypeList::iterator it = p.begin();
00098         param = *it;
00099         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"an1");
00100         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"av1");
00101 
00102         p = data2.GetSummaryParams();
00103         it = p.begin();
00104         param = *it;
00105         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"sn1");
00106         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"sv1");
00107 
00108 
00109         data2.GetQuantificationEntry(0, e);
00110         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.quantification, 10.0f, 0.0001f);
00111         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "abc");
00112         data2.GetQuantificationEntry(1, e);
00113         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.quantification, 20.0f, 0.0001f);
00114         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "xyz");
00115 
00116 }
